ISLAMABAD, Aug 03 (APP):President Dr Arif Alvi Monday summoned the Majlis-e-Shoora (Parliament) in joint sitting to meet on Thursday, August 6, at 5 p.m. in the Parliament House.
He summoned the joint session in exercise of the powers conferred by Clause (1) of Article 54 of the Constitution.
